   ▪ For normal files (e.g., .js, .py, .css, .ts):
   ```
// --- Changelog ---
// [YYYY-MM-DD]: <Short description of what changed> (auto)
   ```

   ▪ For HTML files:
   ```
<!-- --- Changelog ---
[YYYY-MM-DD]: <Short description of what changed> (auto) -->
   ```

Example:
   ```
// --- Changelog ---
// 2025-11-12: Fixed initialization bug and updated config parser. (auto)
   ```

   or

   ```
<!-- --- Changelog ---
2025-11-12: Updated footer layout and fixed navbar spacing. (auto) -->
   ```
</file_change_policy>

